Task 3.2: Locking Assessment & Table-based Locking

Summary: Evaluated the existing in-memory lock manager and determined it was unsuitable for multi-node SQLite deployments. Implemented a TableLockManager that uses a 'locks' table in the database to coordinate work across multiple NetRunner nodes (e.g., when running under LiteFS).

